jedai_catalog_url(25.10)                              jedai_catalog_url(25.10)

Name
       jedai_catalog_url

Syntax
        jedai_catalog_url <jedai_server_url>

       Type: string

       Default: ""

       Enables  the  AI chat box in the Innovus GUI. You  need to set the fol-
       lowing setting in enc.tcl.

       #set server url

       set jedai_catalog_url <server url>

       After you set the URl, AI icon  is enabled in the GUI:

       On clicking this icon, the following AI Assistant window opens.

